---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";
import Finis from "../components/Finis.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Ariel Messing">
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "About Ariel Messing",
    "description": "About Ariel Messing.",
    "url": new URL("/about", Astro.site).href,
    "isPartOf": {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "Ariel Messing",
      "url": Astro.site?.href,
    },
  })} />
  
  <section class="about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <Heading as="h1">About</Heading>
    </header>
    <Prose>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Ariel.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have spent the last twenty years exploring the craft of software development. 
      </p>
      <p>
        After studying Mathematics and Computer Science, I began my career as a Java developer and eventually moved through roles as a team lead, product manager, and Chief Architect.
      </p>
      <p>
        A few years ago, my wife and I moved to the UK. Our arrival coincided with the start of the pandemic, which I took as an opportunity to return to hands-on engineering and dive into areas of computing I hadn't yet explored, from machine learning to generative art. Currently, I work as a freelance developer focusing on specialized client initiatives and open-source contributions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before freelancing, I was a systems architect and full-stack developer for a project I joined in its startup phase. I stayed through two acquisitions, eventually redesigning the core data flow into a serverless architecture: I developed the prototype, trained the implementation team, and guided the product's direction.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am now looking to bring a perspective that bridges high-level architecture and practical execution back to a larger team where I can contribute to meaningful, complex projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I am not by the keyboard, you can find me baking slow-fermented bread, pizza, and the occasional babka; reading (and writing about) history; or cycling through the English countryside.
      </p>
    </Prose>
    <Finis />
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: var(--width-content);
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
</style>